code: public void marshal(Exchange exchange, Object body, OutputStream out) throws Exception {     SyndFeed feed = ExchangeHelper.convertToMandatoryType(exchange, SyndFeed.class, body).     String xml = RssConverter.feedToXml(feed).     out.write(xml.getBytes()). }
